text: Labahitha is a genus of crevice weavers containing the single species, Labahitha oonopiformis. It was first described by S. L. Zonstein, Yuri M. Marusik & I. L. F. Magalhaes in 2017, and is only found in Malaysia. ==References== ==External links== Category:Filistatidae Category:Monotypic Araneomorphae genera
title: Labahitha
